  "ciliary_role": "Deconjugation of the polyubiquitin chain from centrosomal protein Cep70 and promotes ciliogenesis by inhibiting the tubulin deacetylase activity of HDAC6. Regulation of the docking of basal bodies to the apical plasma membrane. CYLD is also required for proper organization of basal bodies and axenomes (25342559). CYLD may control the centriolar satellites proteostasis by preventing the proteasomal degradation of PCM1 (31067453).",
